CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1956, pg. 3 reads: "Cute 'Honeybunnies' Paraded... and captured the hears of everyone at the fashion show at A. Leo Weil School. Wearing perky spring outfits with sparkling smiles on their faces, some came out in pairs, as a single, or in one instance, as a trio.  Left to right:...Major Reid... "
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Major Reid modeling light colored suit with matching tweed jacket and hat, standing with hand in pocket, on stage in A. Leo Weil school for Easter fashion show
